      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "# [2.0.0] - 2024-10-21\r\n\r\nv2.0.0 is a completely rewrite of this project, with faster speed, better user experience, and possibility for more customization!\r\n\r\n## Breaking changes\r\n\r\n- Image handle. Now provides 2 options, abort export if link to image file is found, or embed them as base64 in markdown. Learn more about \"How\" and \"Why\" in README.\r\n- Upload. Currently only support Git. S3 upload may come back soon :)\r\n- Settings. You will need to review and adjust plugin settings, because v2 has made many changes to it.\r\n\r\n## Highlights\r\n\r\n- Much faster and accurate transformation. Use Obsidian's metadata instead of parsing by myself.\r\n- User Confirmation. Now before starting to upload, and before pushing to remote Git repository, there will be a \"summary\" modal that shows which will be exported.\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/yy4382/obsidian-static-site-export/compare/1.3.3...2.0.0",
